high_descs: Turn around and go to the shelf on the right.
Pick up the game controller on the left of the bottom shelf.
Turn around and go straight to the sidetable.
Place the controller on the sidetable.
Turn back around towards the microwave.
Pick up the other controller from the bottom shelf.
Turn around and go back to the sidetable.
Place the second controller on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two Controller on a SideTable.

high_descs: Turn around and find your way to the wooden shelf.
Pick up the game controller from the lower rack.
Turn around and find your way to the wooden sidetable and sofa.
Place the controller on the sidetable.
Turn around and find your way to the microwave.
Open the microwave and take out the controller and close it.
Turn around and then turn right to go to the sidetable.
Place the controller on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Find the controller and place it on the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn towards your left and head towards a shelf.
Take a controller from the rack.
Turn your back and walk towards the sidetable.
Place the controller on the sidetable.
Turn your back and walk towards the microwave.
Take a controller from the plate which is placed inside the oven.
Turn your back and move towards the sidetable.
Place the controller next to the first joystick on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the Controller on the SideTable
